eration Resource with which a Large Load proposes to co-locate. The form may be submitted any time after an LLI number has been assigned to the Large Load project, but ERCOT will not begin its study of the net metering arrangement until the Resource Entity has submitted all information  ...    must submit a Notice of Proposed Net Metering Arrangement form and receive Public Utility Commission approval following an ERCOT study before implementing the net metering arrangement. This file was updated on September 19, 2025 to include  ...    Sep 19, 2025 - pdf - 138.7 KB\n\nQuestions and Answers About the Large Load Interconnection Process This document provides information in a question-and-answer format about the process for interconnecting a Large Load to the ERCOT transmission system. Dec 24, 2025 - pdf -"
